component.illusobjdesc:
At the bottom of the plate, the third design from the left depicts a figure facing down, its body 
                     slightly curved and perhaps falling.  One or both arms are raised vertically (in relation to the figure's head); 
                     the figure appears to rest its head in the crook of its arm.  Its legs are together.
